com.sleepycat.client

Class SMultiStats

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sleepycat.client.SMultiStats

  • public class SMultiStats
extends java.lang.Object
    A SMultiStats contains multiple statistics for a database environment. If a statistics is not available (e.g. not retrieved), null is returned for that statistics.
